13. Qf3
{ This move allows for long castle but the queen does very little here. } 13...
O-O
{ Black finishes development and now threatens Nxd4, hitting the queen and the bishop on b5. }
14. Bxc6 { Avoiding Black's threat. } 14... bxc6 15. g5
