{ After  18.Nb3  Qc7  followed by Rd8 or O-O-O Black's safer king and the pair of bishops offer him great compensation. }
18... Qxc6
{ Black wants to make use of the activity of his rooks with Rh1 or Rd8. } 19.
Qe2 O-O-O
{ Preventing White from castling. Black's activity gives him more than enough compensation for the pawn. }
