{ The black queen keeps an eye on the knight on d4. } 18. b3
{ Covering the c4-square. } 18... Nc6
{ Seeking to exchange the centralised knight as the knight on e5 didn't have prospects with the c4-square covered. Black is quite comfortable here as he has a better structure and his king is safe in the centre. He would like to play an endgame as then he could use the weakness of White's h-pawn. }
