16. Nd4 Nc4
{ The typical jump that forces the exchange of one of White's bishops. } 17.
Ndb5
{ Taking on c4 is worse, as  17.Bxc4  Qxc4  allows Black to follow up with b5-b4 with an attack on the queenside. }
