{ White has a solid set-up on the third rank. He wants to play Qf3 and then decide where to castle. Black now finds an object to attack. Which one? }
9... a5
{ The hapless knight escaped from d4 in order not to be attacked by ...e5, but it doesn't find peace on b3 either! Black doesn't only harass the knight, he also wants to weaken White's dark squares on the queenside by pushing ...a3. In case White stops the advance of the a-pawn with  10.a4  , Black's knight will find a comfortable spot with  10...Nb4  . }
