{ It appears that Black misplayed the opening and is pushed back, but in fact, he has a very strong sacrifice at his disposal. Which one? }
14... Nxe4 15. Nxe4 Bxf5
{ Black's pieces exert very strong pressure on White's position: the knight on e4 is hanging and it cannot escape because the pawn on c2 is under attack too. Black also has the threat of ...d5-d4, which will regain the sacrificed material. }
