[White "9. Strategy and Tactics"]
[Black "The ...Nxe4 Idea #2"]
[Result "*"]
[FEN "r1bq1rk1/1p2bppp/3ppn2/2n5/p1BNPP2/2N1BQ2/PPP3PP/R4RK1 b - - 0 12"]
[SetUp "1"]

{ White seems to have a solid position in the centre. However, his bishop on c4 is somewhat exposed and Black can take advantage of that to obtain a good position. Can you spot the small tactic? }
12... Nfxe4
{ The idea is to lure the queen to e4 in order to make use of the fork with ...d5. }
13. Nxe4 Nxe4 14. Qxe4 d5
{ Black regains the piece and remains with the pair of bishops. } *

